text: Soni pandema jayaliji nkwagwila ilagasyo ŵatiji: “E mmwe Musa! Tuŵendelani kwa Ambuje ŵenu ligongo lya chilanga Chakwe chaŵataŵene namwe (chanti chatutyochesye ilagasyo naga tukulupilile), chisimu naga nkututyochesya ilagasyo, chitunkulupilile kwene soni chitwaleche kwene kuŵigula nomwe ŵanache ŵa Israila.”
